Name: Ancient Astra (Transition)
Desc:
[Enchant Force]
Materializes an arrow of the legends to bombard enemies with a powerful attack.
Enables you to move forward and backward while attacking.

H.Old:
Relic Gauge Cost: 65 per sec. Hold the Skill key to strike 4 enemies at 360% damage 6 times.
Decrease shooting damage that includes the attack proportional to the max HP during the attack by 60%.
Cooldown 60 secs
H.New:
Relic Gauge Cost: 65 per 1 sec. Periodically attacks up to 4 enemies at 360% Damage 6 times in a row.
Damage TAKEN -60% including Max HP-based Damage
Cooldown: 60 sec.
